Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:28.82,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}這暗藍色的混凝土
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:31.30,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}冰冷地將我包裹
Comment: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.76,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}Call my name and give me a kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.76,0:21:36.28,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}而後將我攬入胸懷
